)|Nicolosi]]\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 7 November 1937\n|round=\n|team1 = [[Genoa Cricket and Football Club|Genoa 1937]]\n|team2 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|score  = 1-1\n|report=\n|location= [[Genova]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Luigi Ferraris]]\n|referee = Giuseppe Scarpi\n|goals1 = [[Carlos Servetti|Servetti]] {{Goal|44}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|35}} [[Pietro Ferraris|Ferraris II]]\n|result=D\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 14 November 1937\n|round=\n|team1 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|team2 = [[Juventus]]\n|score  = 2-1\n|report=\n|location = [[Milano]]\n|stadium = [[Arena Civica]]\n|referee = Renzo Curradi\n|goals1 = [[Pietro Ferraris|Ferraris II]] {{Goal|55}}<br />[[Giovanni Ferrari|Ferrari]] {{Goal|81}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|63|pen}} [[Alfredo Foni|Foni]]\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 21 November 1937\n|round=\n|team1 = [[S.S. Lazio|Lazio]]\n|team2 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|score  = 1-3\n|report=\n|location = [[Rome|Roma]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Nazionale|Stadio Nazionale del PNF]]\n|referee = Raffaele Scorzoni\n|goals1 = [[Umberto Busani|Busani]] {{Goal|55|pen}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|4}} [[Pietro Ferraris|Ferraris II]]<br />{{Goal|50}} [[Giuseppe Meazza|Meazza]]<br />{{Goal|81}} [[Nicola Ferrara|Ferrara I]]\n|result = W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 28 November 1937\n|round=\n|team1 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|team2 = Liguria\n|score  = 2-1\n|report=\n|location = [[Milano]]\n|stadium = [[Arena Civica]]\n|referee = Emiliano Saracini\n|goals1 = [[Pietro Ferraris|Ferraris II]] {{Goal|29||87}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|65}} [[Angelo Bollano|Bollano]]\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 12 December 1937\n|round=\n|team1 = [[Atalanta B.C.|Atalanta]]\n|team2 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|score  = 1-1\n|report=\n|location = [[Bergamo]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Atleti Azzurri d'Italia|Stadio Mario Brumana]]\n|referee = Mario Ciamberlini\n|goals1 = [[Severo Cominelli|Cominelli]] {{Goal|63}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|68}} [[Giovanni Ferrari|Ferrari]]\n|result=D\n}}\n{