sto Tomasi|Tomasi]] {{Goal|36}}<br />[[Alfredo Foni|Foni]] {{Goal|86|rig.}}\n|goals2 = \n|result=L\n}}\n\n=== Mitropa Cup ===\n{{main|1938 Mitropa Cup}}\n\n==== Eightfinals ====\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 26 June 1938\n|round=\n|team1 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|team2 = {{flagicon|HUN}}[[Honved]]\n|score = 4-2\n|report=\n|location = [[Milano]]\n|stadium = [[Arena Civica]]\n|Arbitro = [[Dionisi-Nicolae Xifando|Xifando]]\n|Nazarbitro = ROU 1881-1947\n|goals1 = [[Pietro Ferraris|Ferraris II]] {{Goal|67||76}}<br />[[Giuseppe Meazza|Meazza]] {{Goal|75}}<br />[[Giovanni Ferrari|Ferrari]] {{Goal|81}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|19}} [[K\u00e1roly D\u00e9ri|D\u00e9ri]]<br />{{Goal|21}} [[S\u00e1ndor Olajk\u00e1r|Olajk\u00e1r]]\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 2 July 1938\n|round=\n|team1 = {{flagicon|HUN}}[[Honved]]\n|team2 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|score = 1-1\n|report=\n|location = [[Budapest]]\n|stadium = [[Albert Fl\u00f3ri\u00e1n Stadion|\u00dcll\u0151i \u00fati stadion]]\n|referee = {{flagicon|CSK}}Gustav Krist\n|goals1 = [[L\u00e1szl\u00f3 Varga|Varga]] {{Goal|66}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|40|rig.}} [[Giuseppe Meazza|Meazza]]\n|result=D\n}}\n==== Quarterfinals ====\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 11 July 1938\n|round=\n|team1 = {{flagicon|SLK}}[[Slavia Prague]]\n|team2 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|score = 9-0\n|report=\n|location = [[Prague]]\n|stadium = [[Stadi\u00f3n Slavia]]\n|referee = {{flagicon|HUN}}[[P\u00e1l von Hertzka|von Hertzka]]\n|goals1 = [[Josef Bican|Bican]] {{Goal|32||54||60||69}}<br />[[V\u00e1clav Hor\u00e1k|Hor\u00e1k]] {{Goal|34||61}}<br />[[Rudolf Vytla\u010dil|Vytla\u010dil]] {{Goal|48||74}}<br />[[Vojt\u011bch Brad\u00e1\u010d|Brad\u00e1\u010d]] {{Goal|59}}\n|goals2 = \n|result=L\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 17 July 1938\n|round=\n|team1 = Ambrosiana-Inter\n|team2 = {{flagicon|SLK}}[[Slavia Prague]]\n|score = 3-1\n|report=\n|location = [[Milano]]\n|stadium = [[Arena Civica]]\n|referee = {{flagicon|HUN}}[[Mih\u00e1ly Iv\u00e1ncsics|Ivancsi